Forum or Announcement";s:15:"addforum_choose";s:74:"Choose the forum type — you will be taken to the standard creation form.";s:24:"forum_type_general_title";s:18:"General Discussion";s:23:"forum_type_general_desc";s:72:"Open forum — teachers and students can start threads and reply freely.";s:21:"forum_type_news_title";s:13:"Announcements";s:20:"forum_type_news_desc";s:65:"One-way channel. Only teachers post; students read and subscribe.";s:22:"forum_type_qanda_title";s:15:"Q &amp; A Forum";s:21:"forum_type_qanda_desc";s:68:"Students must post their own response before seeing others' replies.";s:21:"forum_type_blog_title";s:16:"Blog-style Forum";s:20:"forum_type_blog_desc";s:67:"Each post is a standalone blog entry. Good for personal reflection.";s:23:"forum_type_single_title";s:17:"Single Discussion";s:22:"forum_type_single_desc";s:66:"One shared topic for the whole class — ideal for focused debate.";s:25:"forum_type_eachuser_title";s:32:"Each Person Posts One Discussion";s:24:"forum_type_eachuser_desc";s:58:"Every student starts exactly one thread; others can reply.";s:20:"quiz_created_success";s:45:"Quiz "{$a}" created. Add questions to it now.";s:19:"quiz_cloned_success";s:50:"Quiz cloned into the lesson with {$a} question(s).";s:10:"filter_all";s:3:"All";s:10:"close_form";s:10:"Close Form";s:18:"upload_new_content";s:18:"Upload New Content";s:16:"upload_pick_type";s:57:"Pick a content type — the form adapts to what you need.";s:18:"upload_change_type";s:6:"change";s:15:"ctype_pdf_title";s:12:"PDF Document";s:14:"ctype_pdf_desc";s:43:"Upload a PDF lesson, worksheet, or reading.";s:19:"ctype_youtube_title";s:13:"YouTube Video";s:18:"ctype_youtube_desc";s:42:"Paste a YouTube link to embed and discuss.";s:17:"ctype_video_title";s:10:"Video File";s:16:"ctype_video_desc";s:34:"Upload an MP4/WebM/MOV video file.";s:17:"ctype_audio_title";s:5:"Audio";s:16:"ctype_audio_desc";s:37:"Upload an audio file (MP3, WAV, OGG).";s:17:"ctype_image_title";s:5:"Image";s:16:"ctype_image_desc";s:37:"Upload an image (JPG, PNG, GIF, SVG).";s:20:"ctype_document_title";s:8:"Document";s:19:"ctype_document_desc";s:41:"Upload a Word, Excel, or Office document.";s:24:"ctype_presentation_title";s:12:"Presentation";s:23:"ctype_presentation_desc";s:38:"Upload a slideshow or PowerPoint file.";s:16:"ctype_book_title";s:12:"Book / eBook";s:15:"ctype_book_desc";s:39:"Upload an EPUB or multi-page book file.";s:16:"ctype_link_title";s:13:"External Link";s:15:"ctype_link_desc";s:42:"Add any external educational resource URL.";s:18:"upload_label_title";s:5:"Title";s:20:"upload_label_subject";s:18:"Subject (optional)";s:17:"upload_subject_ph";s:26:"e.g. Math, Arabic, Science";s:17:"upload_label_file";s:11:"Choose file";s:16:"upload_label_url";s:3:"URL";s:24:"upload_label_youtube_url";s:11:"YouTube URL";s:19:"upload_youtube_hint";s:122:"A valid YouTube link looks like <code>https://youtu.be/XXXXXXX</code> or <code>https://youtube.com/watch?v=XXXXXXX</code>.";s:24:"upload_label_description";s:11:"Description";s:21:"upload_label_keywords";s:8:"Keywords";s:18:"upload_keywords_ph";s:22:"comma, separated, tags";s:20:"upload_submit_review";s:17:"Submit for Review";s:20:"addquiz_tab_homework";s:15:"Upload Homework";s:21:"homework_create_title";s:26:"Create Homework Assignment";s:20:"homework_create_desc";s:113:"Upload a document (PDF, Word, Image) and allow students to submit their work via file upload or rich text editor.";s:20:"homework_title_label";s:14:"Homework Title";s:17:"homework_title_ph";s:25:"e.g., Chapter 4 Exercises";s:19:"homework_desc_label";s:37:"Description / Instructions (Optional)";s:16:"homework_desc_ph";s:43:"Provide any additional instructions here...";s:19:"homework_file_label";s:36:"Homework Document (PDF, Image, Word)";s:18:"homework_file_hint";s:45:"Drag and drop files here, or click to browse.";s:22:"homework_duedate_label";s:19:"Due Date (Optional)";s:25:"homework_submission_types";s:26:"Allowed Submission Methods";s:24:"homework_submission_fil